  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bank
    This class models a Bank building to be placed in the city.
    Building
    This class serves as the foundation and base model for any kind of specific building created to be placed in the city.
    Factory
    This class models a Factory building to be placed in the city.
    GasStation
    This class models a Gas Station building to be placed in the city.
    GeneralStore
    This class models a General Store building to be placed in the city, which supposedly sells all non-food related necessities and luxuries.
    GovBuilding
    This class models a Government or capital building to be placed in the city.
    GroceryStore
    This class models a Grocery Store building to be placed in the city.
    Hospital
    This class models a Hospital building to be placed in the city.
    Library
    This class models a public Library building to be placed in the city.
    Neighborhood
    This class models a Neighborhood, representative of 3 houses, to be placed in the city.
    Park
    This class models a Park structure to be placed in the city.
    Plaza
    This class models a Plaza structure, which consists of entertainment and other leisurely activities, to be placed in the city.
    PowerPlant
    This class models a Power plant building, which supplies energy, to be placed in the city.
    School
    This class models a School building, covering all grade levels, to be placed in the city.
